<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="PlenOctrees for Real-time Rendering of Neural Radiance Fields">
  <data key="d0">PlenOctrees for Real-time Rendering of Neural Radiance Fields</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">PlenOctrees for Real-time Rendering of Neural Radiance Fields is a paper published on 2021-03-25 that presents PlenOctrees as a sparse octree-based representation for accelerating Neural Radiance Fields rendering.</data>
