  <data key="d2">Stability AI is an organization credited with the TripoSR paper alongside VAST AI Research.&lt;SEP&gt;Stability AI is one of the organizations that collaboratively developed TripoSR.&lt;SEP&gt;Stability AI is the organization identified as the developer of Threestudio.</data>
