<node id="Single Image">
  <data key="d0">Single Image</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Single Image is the input data used by TripoSR for 3D object reconstruction.&lt;SEP&gt;Single Image is the input form used by TripoSR for feedforward 3D reconstruction.&lt;SEP&gt;Single Image is the input from which DreamGaussian produces a textured mesh.&lt;SEP&gt;Single Image is the input data used by Zero-1-to-3 for viewpoint-conditioned novel view synthesis.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-21872029f2f74d4a8d748cb5926862f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc465068a32c3c5f3d12d7446a5843df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8d7bbefe39a52948bd9d7195856ac2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c47e36db5dfb4966f1d4d610b06ac6bc</data>
