</node>
<node id="Triplane Representation">
  <data key="d0">Triplane Representation</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Triplane Representation is the intermediate representation produced by the transformer encoder in TripoSR.&lt;SEP&gt;Triplane representation is the intermediate representation predicted by the deep cross-attention transformer in the Large Reconstruction Model to parameterise the output radiance field.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-21872029f2f74d4a8d748cb5926862f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-faebadc81c39822f071629969e8b6a2b</data>
