<node id="Diffusion-Based 3D Generation">
  <data key="d0">Diffusion-Based 3D Generation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diffusion-Based 3D Generation is a subtopic of the weekly synthesis and concerns 3D generation methods built from diffusion-model-based guidance and reconstruction.&lt;SEP&gt;Diffusion-Based 3D Generation is the sub-topic under which ProlificDreamer is categorized.&lt;SEP&gt;Diffusion-Based 3D Generation is a sub-topic focused on creating 3D assets using diffusion-model-based priors and optimization methods.&lt;SEP&gt;Diffusion-based 3D generation is the broader area in which DreamFusion's core idea remains a foundational primitive.&lt;SEP&gt;Diffusion-Based 3D Generation is the sub-topic assigned to the Magic123 Paper.&lt;SEP&gt;Diffusion-Based 3D Generation is the sub-topic under which Zero-1-to-3 is categorized.&lt;SEP&gt;Diffusion-Based 3D Generation is the subtopic under which DreamGaussian is categorized in the input metadata.</data>
