  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Generative 3D Representations is a subtopic of the weekly synthesis and concerns learned representations used to generate 3D assets or scenes.&lt;SEP&gt;Generative 3D Representations is the sub-topic under which the Instant3D paper is categorized.&lt;SEP&gt;Generative 3D Representations is the sub-topic assigned to the paper.&lt;SEP&gt;Generative 3D Representations is the sub-topic under which the paper is categorized.</data>
