  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Dynamic And 4D Reconstruction is a subtopic of the weekly synthesis and refers to reconstruction methods for dynamic or time-varying 3D content.&lt;SEP&gt;Dynamic and 4D Reconstruction is the sub-topic under which HyperNeRF is categorized.&lt;SEP&gt;Dynamic And 4D Reconstruction is the sub-topic under which the paper is categorized.&lt;SEP&gt;Dynamic And 4D Reconstruction is the sub-topic under which the paper is categorized.</data>
