  <data key="d0">DreamGaussian Repository</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">DreamGaussian Repository is the official implementation repository for DreamGaussian: Generative Gaussian Splatting for Efficient 3D Content Creation, mirrored as README text without code on 2026-05-15 under the MIT license.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c813fde1299cbc52bb51e88942b07033</data>
