  <data key="d2">DreamGaussian: Generative Gaussian Splatting for Efficient 3D Content Creation is the canonical paper associated with the repository and is linked through Arxiv.&lt;SEP&gt;DreamGaussian: Generative Gaussian Splatting for Efficient 3D Content Creation is the canonical paper associated with the repository and DreamGaussian implementation.</data>
