  <data key="d0">Image-To-3D</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Image-To-3D is a usage mode of the repository that preprocesses input images and trains Gaussian and mesh stages to create 3D outputs.&lt;SEP&gt;Image-To-3D is a workflow that generates 3D content from an input image and is described with multiple configuration options.</data>
