  <data key="d2">Text-To-3D is a usage mode referenced through the Colab demo for the repository.&lt;SEP&gt;Text-To-3D is a workflow that generates 3D content from a text prompt and is described with dedicated configuration files.&lt;SEP&gt;Text-To-3D is a method listed for Magic3D and describes the generation of 3D content from text prompts.</data>
