<node id="Main.py">
  <data key="d0">Main.py</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Main.py is the script used for the Gaussian training stage, GUI visualization, checkpoint loading, and elevation-controlled training in the Image-To-3D workflow.&lt;SEP&gt;Main.py is the primary script used to train, test, visualize, and export outputs for text-conditioned and image-conditioned 3D generation workflows.&lt;SEP&gt;Main.py is a Python script used in the example commands for image-based testing, GUI execution, and debugging-related runs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c813fde1299cbc52bb51e88942b07033&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fbd6ef7fa46c0ba5c1daac3eb1cafc5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89b96bffec912e64ed752226976c3822</data>
