  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Mildenhall Et Al., 2020 is the cited authorship and publication reference for NeRF: Representing Scenes as Neural Radiance Fields for View Synthesis.&lt;SEP&gt;Mildenhall Et Al., 2020 is the prior work cited as the source of NeRF that NeRF-W extends to unconstrained photo collections.&lt;SEP&gt;Mildenhall et al., 2020 is the referenced prior work that introduced the standard NeRF used in canonical template space within Nerfies.</data>
