  <data key="d5">1778876010</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="BARF">
  <data key="d0">BARF</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">BARF is a later NeRF paper in the corpus that compares against the bmild/nerf baseline.&lt;SEP&gt;BARF is a 2021 paper on bundle-adjusting NeRF that jointly optimizes camera poses with the field using a coarse-to-fine positional encoding schedule.</data>
