  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">graphdeco-inria/gaussian-splatting is the reference implementation associated with 3D Gaussian Splatting and is described as non-commercial.&lt;SEP&gt;graphdeco-inria/gaussian-splatting is a repository whose mirrored README describes the official authors' implementation associated with the paper on 3D Gaussian Splatting and notes that the mirror includes only README text, not code.&lt;SEP&gt;graphdeco-inria/gaussian-splatting is a repository that serves as the official implementation of 3D Gaussian Splatting for Real-Time Radiance Field Rendering and provides reference components used by downstream 3DGS methods.</data>
