  <data key="d0">Gsplat Math Supplement</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Gsplat Math Supplement is a paper supplement recommended alongside the original 3D Gaussian Splatting paper because the projection math is more subtle than the rasteriser code suggests.</data>
