  <data key="d2">Benjamin Recht is an author of the paper introducing K-Planes.&lt;SEP&gt;Benjamin Recht is an author of Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks.&lt;SEP&gt;Benjamin Recht is an author of Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-135c075dc7391afb1b0d603462e342e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95e7570668ab2add22a107c42e84d859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0561cfd70b96f995d3cdeb043981668</data>
