<node id="UNISURF: Unifying Neural Implicit Surfaces and Radiance Fields for Multi-View Reconstruction">
  <data key="d0">UNISURF: Unifying Neural Implicit Surfaces and Radiance Fields for Multi-View Reconstruction</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">UNISURF: Unifying Neural Implicit Surfaces and Radiance Fields for Multi-View Reconstruction is a paper published on 2021-04-20 that presents the UNISURF method.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65491bb40aaff28e47124705eb1fff58</data>
