  <data key="d2">Andreas Geiger is an author of the UNISURF paper.&lt;SEP&gt;Andreas Geiger is an author of the paper MVSplat: Efficient 3D Gaussian Splatting from Sparse Multi-View Images.&lt;SEP&gt;Andreas Geiger is an author of MonoSDF.&lt;SEP&gt;Andreas Geiger is an author of MERF.&lt;SEP&gt;Andreas Geiger is an author of 2D Gaussian Splatting for Geometrically Accurate Radiance Fields.</data>
