  <data key="d0">sxyu/svox2</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">sxyu/svox2 is a repository mirror whose README describes the Plenoxels project and states that the mirror contains only README text rather than code.&lt;SEP&gt;sxyu/svox2 is a repository that contains the reference implementation of Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks and is distributed as the `svox2` library.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-95e7570668ab2add22a107c42e84d859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eaaf691c43304c4a589967639d84b94f</data>
