  <data key="d5">1778876204</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks">
  <data key="d0">Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks is a work associated with the repository, an official optimization codebase, a website, a video, an arXiv entry, and a CVPR citation.&lt;SEP&gt;Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks is a paper that presents an explicit radiance field representation that matches NeRF-quality view synthesis without using a neural network.&lt;SEP&gt;Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks is the paper for which sxyu/svox2 serves as the reference implementation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-95e7570668ab2add22a107c42e84d859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0561cfd70b96f995d3cdeb043981668&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eaaf691c43304c4a589967639d84b94f</data>
