  <data key="d0">UC Berkeley</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">UC Berkeley is the institutional affiliation listed with the Plenoxels work.&lt;SEP&gt;UC Berkeley is listed as one of the institutes from which project contributors come.&lt;SEP&gt;UC Berkeley is an institutional affiliation listed for several authors of the NeRF paper.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-95e7570668ab2add22a107c42e84d859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bfb5c9e689ffa78ae20907ec96c23e19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee99e1fe0369d50218c77432ff216939</data>
