</node>
<node id="Ninja">
  <data key="d0">Ninja</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Ninja is a tool suggested for installation to enable parallel compilation and improve iteration speed.&lt;SEP&gt;Ninja is a build tool suggested to accelerate installation of native extensions through parallel compilation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-02c51c541bd8838daa93cb2a36760941&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333901bdf7c8210583cee57303d02eb3</data>
