</node>
<node id="Ubuntu">
  <data key="d0">Ubuntu</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Ubuntu is the operating system on which Ninja can be installed with the `sudo apt install ninja-build` command.&lt;SEP&gt;Ubuntu is the operating system on which `ninja-build` is suggested to be installed with `apt`.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-02c51c541bd8838daa93cb2a36760941&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333901bdf7c8210583cee57303d02eb3</data>
