<node id="Neural-SLAM">
  <data key="d0">Neural-SLAM</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Neural-SLAM is the line of SLAM systems based on implicit feature grids or point-cloud feature stores with NeRF-style volume rendering supervision.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32b6f8bef5969e289e4fe3c770fb5f73</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/weekly/2026-W17/synthesis.md</data>
