  <data key="d0">Diffusion-Into-3D Line</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diffusion-Into-3D Line is one of the two threads to follow into W18 and is linked to DreamGaussian bridging into the splatting representation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4716f0532d6b5d940a3893a269cfdc9</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/weekly/2026-W17/synthesis.md</data>
