</node>
<node id="latentSplat">
  <data key="d0">latentSplat</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">latentSplat is a 2024 work by Wewer et al. that feed-forward predicts Gaussian parameters from sparse-view inputs and removes per-scene optimisation.&lt;SEP&gt;latentSplat is a feed-forward Gaussian predictor included in the family of methods for which MVSplat has become a reference point.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4716f0532d6b5d940a3893a269cfdc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26c994414b7985eeccba7c9a66fd05d3</data>
