  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">VAST-AI-Research/TripoSR is the official codebase repository for TripoSR and is mirrored in the provided text as README content only.&lt;SEP&gt;VAST-AI-Research/TripoSR is the open-source repository associated with TripoSR.</data>
