</node>
<node id="CUDA">
  <data key="d0">CUDA</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">CUDA is an optional platform dependency whose locally installed major version must match the PyTorch-shipped CUDA major version.&lt;SEP&gt;CUDA is the GPU build and execution technology used by default for extensions and acceleration, though some optional paths avoid requiring it.&lt;SEP&gt;CUDA is the acceleration technology used by gsplat and is also part of supported installation combinations for pre-compiled wheels.&lt;SEP&gt;CUDA is a recent required dependency with recommended tested versions for Windows and Linux.&lt;SEP&gt;CUDA is the GPU software stack that may need updating and correct configuration in order for Instant-NGP to compile successfully.&lt;SEP&gt;CUDA is a required software platform that must be installed for DROID-SLAM, and its version is expected to match the major version of PyTorch.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc465068a32c3c5f3d12d7446a5843df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0ea2d1fff273acbdf62338200407400&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f175249759ca8a973f8918ff16dfac34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67aca36ec8eb49d9f01fa3055f69d8fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b9702cfd82aaa0f9d50ba7409bbecf8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-833bec7f18854880457df56d1a16dbb7</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/vast-ai-research-triposr/readme.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/ashawkey-stable-dreamfusion/readme.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nerfstudio-project-gsplat/readme.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nvlabs-instant-ngp/readme.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/princeton-vl-droid-slam/readme.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876658</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="setuptools">
  <data key="d0">setuptools</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">setuptools is a dependency that should be upgraded and must meet a minimum version requirement during troubleshooting.&lt;SEP&gt;setuptools is a Python packaging utility that is required at version 49.6.0 or higher.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc465068a32c3c5f3d12d7446a5843df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c7d76e53023a8dbf570b925a45a1d01</data>
