  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">RealTimeRendering is the method listed in the metadata of Direct Sparse Odometry Paper.&lt;SEP&gt;RealTimeRendering is a method listed for the paper and relates to the interactive rendering-based operation of Co-SLAM.&lt;SEP&gt;RealTimeRendering is the real-time rendering regime that the paper targets for dynamic radiance fields.</data>
