<node id="MVSplat: Efficient 3D Gaussian Splatting from Sparse Multi-View Images">
  <data key="d0">MVSplat: Efficient 3D Gaussian Splatting from Sparse Multi-View Images</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">MVSplat: Efficient 3D Gaussian Splatting from Sparse Multi-View Images is a paper published on 2024-03-21 that presents MVSplat as an efficient feed-forward approach for predicting 3D Gaussian splatting parameters from sparse multi-view images.</data>
