</node>
<node id="NVlabs/instant-ngp">
  <data key="d0">NVlabs/instant-ngp</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">NVlabs/instant-ngp is the codebase described as the reference implementation of the method.&lt;SEP&gt;NVlabs/instant-ngp is the reference codebase for Instant-NGP and is described as having been ported into more downstream systems than any other codebase in the corpus.&lt;SEP&gt;NVlabs/instant-ngp is NVIDIA's reference implementation of Instant Neural Graphics Primitives with a Multiresolution Hash Encoding, and the corpus mirrors only its README while omitting the code.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-71173d9786b13b28dc182e4c921d912b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec770f62777c513047108cb79ba7aa75&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ce2165eaaf1422a9b02235e41e20e20</data>
