</node>
<node id="Stable-Dreamfusion">
  <data key="d0">Stable-Dreamfusion</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Stable-Dreamfusion is a referenced repository for 3D reconstruction and for reconstruction results related to the Janus problem discussion.&lt;SEP&gt;Stable-Dreamfusion is a project that implements 3D reconstruction with zero123.&lt;SEP&gt;Stable-Dreamfusion is a PyTorch implementation of the text-to-3D model Dreamfusion and is powered by the Stable Diffusion text-to-2D model.&lt;SEP&gt;Stable-Dreamfusion is the project directory and software system in which extensions can be built and text-to-3D training commands are run.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0d057f3bc5fa56c4a6477fe9f9195f8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1cb4f77562fea889c9e32a8c9b6b118&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cee14ff0001178656f392a3bf199e70c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0ea2d1fff273acbdf62338200407400</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/cvlab-columbia-zero123/readme.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/ashawkey-stable-dreamfusion/readme.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778875659</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="SDS Loss">
  <data key="d0">SDS Loss</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">SDS Loss is a loss method used by Stable-Dreamfusion together with zero123 for 3D reconstruction.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0d057f3bc5fa56c4a6477fe9f9195f8b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/cvlab-columbia-zero123/readme.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778875428</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Training Script">
  <data key="d0">Training Script</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The training script is a preliminary procedure for training the model with a specified configuration, checkpoint, and multi-GPU setup.&lt;SEP&gt;Training Script is a released resource for the Zero-1-to-3 project described as preliminary.&lt;SEP&gt;The training script is invoked with `python train.py` using a TartanAir datapath, GPU count, and learning rate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0d057f3bc5fa56c4a6477fe9f9195f8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1cb4f77562fea889c9e32a8c9b6b118&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-589b580dce9f23cba1db6f4f68a4ae77</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/cvlab-columbia-zero123/readme.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/princeton-vl-droid-slam/readme.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876659</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Objaverse Renderings">
  <data key="d0">Objaverse Renderings</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Objaverse renderings are a downloadable rendering dataset released for use in the project.&lt;SEP&gt;Objaverse Renderings is a released dataset resource associated with the Zero-1-to-3 project.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0d057f3bc5fa56c4a6477fe9f9195f8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1cb4f77562fea889c9e32a8c9b6b118</data>
