  <data key="d0">Bernhard Kerbl</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Bernhard Kerbl is an author of the paper 3D Gaussian Splatting for Real-Time Radiance Field Rendering and is marked as an equal contributor.&lt;SEP&gt;Bernhard Kerbl is an author of 3D Gaussian Splatting for Real-Time Radiance Field Rendering.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41e2a18164d88d58975577aab63d7325&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d445282e0f2225e2a32ef51280563a09</data>
