<node id="Pre-Trained Models">
  <data key="d0">Pre-Trained Models</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Pre-trained models are resources provided by the repository in addition to reference images.&lt;SEP&gt;Pre-Trained Models are downloadable models created with the release codebase and require corresponding source data sets for evaluation.&lt;SEP&gt;Pre-Trained Models are models whose download location can be provided so that training can be skipped during full evaluation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41e2a18164d88d58975577aab63d7325&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eadedf8ea91fdbae049617371c868a2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ace087a61df1fdd6d045f0f39a3166c</data>
