  <data key="d0">Established Datasets</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Established datasets are the datasets on which the paper demonstrates state-of-the-art visual quality and real-time rendering.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41e2a18164d88d58975577aab63d7325</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/readme.md</data>
