<node id="train.py">
  <data key="d0">train.py</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">train.py is the training script used to run the optimizer and accept multiple command-line arguments for training, evaluation, debugging, saving, and checkpointing.&lt;SEP&gt;train.py is the script used to run the optimizer on a COLMAP or NeRF Synthetic dataset.&lt;SEP&gt;train.py is the training script used to train synthetic, DyNeRF, and HyperNeRF scenes with dataset-specific configurations.&lt;SEP&gt;`train.py` is a training script that is run with dataset paths, ports, experiment names, configuration files, and optional checkpoint arguments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0904dcd328c5d8ef13d24665f942dc54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f03bfcd22d34d1827ec44d4dfcce42df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e94987ca7ac98962142f83ef53476d0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d8dc07a758da2f544255725b8c6e1a2</data>
