<node id="White Background">
  <data key="d0">White Background</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">White Background is an optional background setting used instead of the default black background, especially for evaluation of the NeRF Synthetic dataset.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f03bfcd22d34d1827ec44d4dfcce42df</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/readme.md</data>
