  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Deep Blending is a data set for which SfM data sets are provided.&lt;SEP&gt;Deep Blending is a source dataset path required by the evaluation script if training or rendering is performed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eadedf8ea91fdbae049617371c868a2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ace087a61df1fdd6d045f0f39a3166c</data>
