</node>
<node id="Real-Time Viewer">
  <data key="d0">Real-Time Viewer</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Real-Time Viewer is a viewer that can display trained models.&lt;SEP&gt;Real-Time Viewer is one of the two interactive viewers provided for the method and requires CUDA-ready hardware.</data>
