  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">CC-BY-4.0 (LLM-Wiki demo prose) is the license listed for MonoSDF in the metadata.&lt;SEP&gt;CC-BY-4.0 (LLM-Wiki demo prose) is the license associated with the paper metadata.&lt;SEP&gt;CC-BY-4.0 (LLM-Wiki Demo Prose) is the license value listed in the paper metadata.</data>
