</node>
<node id="DeepFloyd-IF">
  <data key="d0">DeepFloyd-IF</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">DeepFloyd-IF is a model for which Perp-Neg support is provided in Stable-Dreamfusion.&lt;SEP&gt;DeepFloyd-IF is a model or software component that requires acceptance of usage conditions and Hugging Face login before use.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-cee14ff0001178656f392a3bf199e70c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0ea2d1fff273acbdf62338200407400</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/ashawkey-stable-dreamfusion/readme.md</data>
