  <data key="d0">Image-Conditioned 3D Generation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Image-Conditioned 3D Generation is a generation mode in Stable-Dreamfusion that requires manually downloaded pretrained checkpoints.&lt;SEP&gt;Image-Conditioned 3D Generation is a workflow that creates 3D results from processed input images and may use different backends depending on the provided inputs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-cee14ff0001178656f392a3bf199e70c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fbd6ef7fa46c0ba5c1daac3eb1cafc5</data>
