  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Work is the project described in the text, including usage commands, debugging guidance, evaluation instructions, and acknowledgements of related research works and open-source projects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-89b96bffec912e64ed752226976c3822</data>
