  <data key="d0">CLIP R-Precision Evaluation</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">CLIP R-Precision Evaluation is an evaluation procedure used to reproduce paper results by testing R-precision between a prompt and an image with R set to 1.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-89b96bffec912e64ed752226976c3822</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/ashawkey-stable-dreamfusion/readme.md</data>
