<node id="Perp-Neg: Re-imagine the Negative Prompt Algorithm: Transform 2D Diffusion into 3D, Alleviate Janus Problem and Beyond">
  <data key="d0">Perp-Neg: Re-imagine the Negative Prompt Algorithm: Transform 2D Diffusion into 3D, Alleviate Janus Problem and Beyond</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Perp-Neg: Re-imagine the Negative Prompt Algorithm: Transform 2D Diffusion into 3D, Alleviate Janus Problem and Beyond is an acknowledged research work about transforming 2D diffusion into 3D and alleviating the Janus problem.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-89b96bffec912e64ed752226976c3822</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/ashawkey-stable-dreamfusion/readme.md</data>
