  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">RealFusion: 360° Reconstruction of Any Object from a Single Image is an acknowledged research work on reconstructing an object in 360 degrees from a single image.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-89b96bffec912e64ed752226976c3822</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/ashawkey-stable-dreamfusion/readme.md</data>
