  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Fantasia3D: Disentangling Geometry and Appearance for High-quality Text-to-3D Content Creation is an acknowledged research work on high-quality text-to-3D content creation through disentangling geometry and appearance.</data>
