  <data key="d0">2311.06214</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">2311.06214 is the arXiv identifier listed for the Instant3D paper.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-22bc14784620637c470939b2097cd200</data>
