<node id="Real Dynamic Scenes">
  <data key="d0">Real Dynamic Scenes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Real dynamic scenes are scenes for which the dataset provided in HyperNeRF is used, and for which the Plenoptic Dataset can also be downloaded and reorganized.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e94987ca7ac98962142f83ef53476d0b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/hustvl-4dgaussians/readme.md</data>
