<node id="Training Config File">
  <data key="d0">Training Config File</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The training config file is a Python configuration file stored under an `arguments` directory and is used to customize training.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5d8dc07a758da2f544255725b8c6e1a2</data>
