  <data key="d0">SyncDreamer</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">SyncDreamer is a follow-up work described as building on the viewpoint-conditional diffusion-model formulation introduced by Zero-1-to-3.&lt;SEP&gt;SyncDreamer is a downstream method in the corpus that depends on the checkpoint and inference scripts from the repository.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7d4bb138a75a3adf4eebfac8bdf1be29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c47e36db5dfb4966f1d4d610b06ac6bc</data>
