</node>
<node id="Wonder3D">
  <data key="d0">Wonder3D</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Wonder3D is a follow-up work described as building on the viewpoint-conditional diffusion-model formulation introduced by Zero-1-to-3.</data>
