</node>
<node id="bmild/nerf">
  <data key="d0">bmild/nerf</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">bmild/nerf is the reference implementation described as the canonical starting point for Neural Radiance Fields.&lt;SEP&gt;bmild/nerf is a mirrored GitHub repository that contains the README for the NeRF project and references the upstream project, code resources, paper, and data.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed61775b026776e3df7ec95d66d9c8df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee99e1fe0369d50218c77432ff216939</data>
