  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">LucidDreamer: Domain-free Generation of 3D Gaussian Splatting Scenes is a paper dated 2023-11-22 that presents a domain-free pipeline for generating large 3D Gaussian Splatting scenes.</data>
