  <data key="d0">arXiv-2112-05131</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">arXiv-2112-05131 is the canonical paper identifier associated with Plenoxels: Radiance Fields without Neural Networks in the repository metadata.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eaaf691c43304c4a589967639d84b94f</data>
