</node>
<node id="SDS">
  <data key="d0">SDS</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">SDS is the method used by DreamGaussian to distill the Zero-1-to-3 image-conditioned diffusion prior.&lt;SEP&gt;SDS is the mechanism through which the 2D diffusion prior supplies novel-view score gradients in the first stage of DreamGaussian.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d585a450d31daf1370ab99c3ececfb44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8d7bbefe39a52948bd9d7195856ac2b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/dreamgaussian-dreamgaussian/about.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2309-16653/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876451</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Image-to-3D Pipeline">
  <data key="d0">Image-to-3D Pipeline</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Image-to-3D Pipeline is the approximately two-minute process produced by DreamGaussian for converting an image into 3D content.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d585a450d31daf1370ab99c3ececfb44</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/dreamgaussian-dreamgaussian/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876217</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Diffusion-based 3D Generation">
  <data key="d0">Diffusion-based 3D Generation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diffusion-based 3D Generation is the section of the corpus that DreamGaussian opened to feed-forward Gaussian generators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d585a450d31daf1370ab99c3ececfb44</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/dreamgaussian-dreamgaussian/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876217</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="arxiv-2309-16653">
  <data key="d0">arxiv-2309-16653</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">arxiv-2309-16653 is the canonical paper identifier associated with the dreamgaussian/dreamgaussian repository.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d585a450d31daf1370ab99c3ececfb44</data>
