</node>
<node id="Revising Densification in Gaussian Splatting">
  <data key="d0">Revising Densification in Gaussian Splatting</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Revising Densification in Gaussian Splatting is a paper that revisits Adaptive Density Control in 3D Gaussian Splatting and proposes a pixel-error-driven formulation for density control together with a correction to opacity handling during cloning.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-add2de44399af98e378bc92e1b3f3d85</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2404-06109/paper.md</data>
