  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Nerfstudio-Project/Gsplat is a GitHub repository mirror that contains the README text for the gsplat project and references the upstream repository, license, and canonical paper.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f175249759ca8a973f8918ff16dfac34</data>
