<node id="Gsplat White Paper">
  <data key="d0">Gsplat White Paper</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Gsplat White Paper is a project paper available on arXiv that includes benchmarking and a mathematical supplement with conventions and derivations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bfb5c9e689ffa78ae20907ec96c23e19</data>
