  <data key="d0">Standard Graphics Pipelines</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Standard Graphics Pipelines are downstream pipelines with which the textured mesh produced by DreamGaussian is compatible.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8d7bbefe39a52948bd9d7195856ac2b</data>
