  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Mathematical Supplement for the Gsplat Library is the mathematical write-up that accompanies Gsplat and is attributed to Ye et al., 2023.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50e33da257497d62c9963654a61913d2</data>
