</node>
<node id="Differentiable Rasterization">
  <data key="d0">Differentiable Rasterization</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Differentiable rasterization is the core computational method of 3D Gaussians that Gsplat re-implements with explicit, documented gradients.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50e33da257497d62c9963654a61913d2</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nerfstudio-project-gsplat/about.md</data>
