  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Docker Compose is the tool used to build and run the `instant-ngp` container from the specified configuration file.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-67aca36ec8eb49d9f01fa3055f69d8fd</data>
