  <data key="d0">Devcontainer Docker Compose File</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Devcontainer Docker Compose File is the `.devcontainer/docker-compose.yml` configuration used to build and run the `instant-ngp` container.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-67aca36ec8eb49d9f01fa3055f69d8fd</data>
