  <data key="d0">`pyngp`</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">`pyngp` is the Python module that may be missing if CMake fails to detect Python or builds the module in a different folder.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-67aca36ec8eb49d9f01fa3055f69d8fd</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nvlabs-instant-ngp/readme.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876504</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
