  <data key="d0">Discussions Board</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Discussions Board is a resource suggested for searching for help.&lt;SEP&gt;The Discussions Board is a support resource recommended for searching unresolved problems related to Instant-NGP.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-67aca36ec8eb49d9f01fa3055f69d8fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d77e66aa7cc152f532934b3e4405857</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nvlabs-instant-ngp/readme.md</data>
