<node id="Multiresolution Hash Input Encoding">
  <data key="d0">Multiresolution Hash Input Encoding</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Multiresolution hash input encoding is the encoding method used by Instant-NGP when training and rendering an MLP.</data>
