  <data key="d0">./instant-ngp</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">./instant-ngp is the executable application for running Instant-NGP and supports a `--no-gui` option for headless mode.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0096ef684fc11385dab039c4985ae213</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nvlabs-instant-ngp/readme.md</data>
