<node id="scripts/run.py">
  <data key="d0">scripts/run.py</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">scripts/run.py is a script that can run the code after a successful build.&lt;SEP&gt;scripts/run.py is a Python script for running Instant-NGP, demonstrating example usage and supporting a superset of the command line arguments of `./instant-ngp`.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0096ef684fc11385dab039c4985ae213&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b9702cfd82aaa0f9d50ba7409bbecf8</data>
