<node id="NeRF Reconstruction">
  <data key="d0">NeRF Reconstruction</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">NeRF reconstruction is discussed in the context of poor results on a custom dataset and possible causes of low quality.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0096ef684fc11385dab039c4985ae213</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nvlabs-instant-ngp/readme.md</data>
