</node>
<node id="Custom Dataset">
  <data key="d0">Custom Dataset</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">A custom dataset is data used for NeRF reconstruction and may produce poor results because of pose reconstruction issues, blur, movement, or suboptimal parameters.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0096ef684fc11385dab039c4985ae213</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nvlabs-instant-ngp/readme.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876505</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="AABB_Scale">
  <data key="d0">AABB_Scale</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">AABB_Scale is a dataset parameter recommended to start at 128 and then be adjusted by factors of two for optimal quality.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0096ef684fc11385dab039c4985ae213</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nvlabs-instant-ngp/readme.md</data>
