  <data key="d0">NeRF Training &amp; Dataset Tips</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">NeRF Training &amp; Dataset Tips is documentation referenced for more information about moving the center of the volume of interest and fine tuning.&lt;SEP&gt;NeRF training and dataset tips are recommended reading for improving dataset quality and training results.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0096ef684fc11385dab039c4985ae213&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b9702cfd82aaa0f9d50ba7409bbecf8</data>
