<node id="Multiresolution Hash Grid Encoding">
  <data key="d0">Multiresolution Hash Grid Encoding</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Multiresolution Hash Grid Encoding is an encoding method introduced by NVlabs/instant-ngp and reused by several later systems in the corpus.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1ce2165eaaf1422a9b02235e41e20e20</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/nvlabs-instant-ngp/about.md</data>
