  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">render_demo.ipynb is a notebook used to render new views from a pretrained NeRF model.&lt;SEP&gt;render_demo.ipynb is a notebook used to render new views from a pretrained high-resolution NeRF for the Fern dataset.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-45d73dd21f95946d74e1b943beb1d384&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee99e1fe0369d50218c77432ff216939</data>
