  <data key="d0">run_nerf.py</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">run_nerf.py is the script used to launch NeRF training with configuration files such as config_fern.txt and config_lego.txt.&lt;SEP&gt;run_nerf.py is a code file that uses the OpenGL pose coordinate system and contains data loading code relevant to pose and camera information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-45d73dd21f95946d74e1b943beb1d384&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee99e1fe0369d50218c77432ff216939</data>
