  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">config_fern.txt is a configuration file used with run_nerf.py to optimize a low-resolution Fern NeRF.&lt;SEP&gt;config_fern.txt is a configuration file presented as an example of settings for a forward-facing scene.</data>
