  <data key="d0">Differentiable Gaussian Rasterization</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Differentiable Gaussian Rasterization is a reference CUDA-kernel-based method introduced by the repository for rendering-related computation in 3DGS.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876956</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Spherical Harmonics View-Dependent Color Model">
  <data key="d0">Spherical Harmonics View-Dependent Color Model</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Spherical Harmonics View-Dependent Color Model is a view-dependent color modeling method introduced by the repository as a reference component for 3DGS.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876956</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Training Pipeline">
  <data key="d0">Training Pipeline</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Training Pipeline is the repository's process for taking a sparse COLMAP SfM point cloud and densifying it into millions of anisotropic 3D Gaussians.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876956</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sparse COLMAP SfM Point Cloud">
  <data key="d0">Sparse COLMAP SfM Point Cloud</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Sparse COLMAP SfM Point Cloud is the input data consumed by the training pipeline before densification.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876956</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Millions of Anisotropic 3D Gaussians">
  <data key="d0">Millions of Anisotropic 3D Gaussians</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Millions of Anisotropic 3D Gaussians are the densified output produced by the training pipeline.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876958</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cross-Graph Linking">
  <data key="d0">Cross-Graph Linking</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Cross-Graph Linking is the demonstrated capability of connecting papers and their canonical implementations within the LLM-Wiki demo corpus.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876958</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Non-Commercial Research Only License">
  <data key="d0">Non-Commercial Research Only License</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Non-Commercial Research Only License is the upstream licensing condition that prevents the code from being redistributed in the LLM-Wiki corpus.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876958</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Reference CUDA Kernels">
  <data key="d0">Reference CUDA Kernels</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Reference CUDA Kernels are the implementation components introduced by the repository for differentiable Gaussian rasterization, adaptive density control, and the spherical harmonics view-dependent color model.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876958</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Downstream 3DGS Method">
  <data key="d0">Downstream 3DGS Method</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Downstream 3DGS Method is a later 3D Gaussian Splatting method that builds on the reference components introduced by the repository.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77bbc3a5c1fbf4a8a4029857b6fa01b</data>
  <data key="d4">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/repos/graphdeco-inria-gaussian-splatting/about.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1778876958</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
