<edge source="NeRF" target="Magic3D">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Magic3D uses a NeRF representation in its first stage before converting it into a mesh for the second stage.&lt;SEP&gt;Magic3D begins with a low-resolution NeRF as the first stage of its coarse-to-fine pipeline.</data>
  <data key="d9">coarse stage,pipeline,representation,stage one</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c0c63708e1adea212beb7d6e83516771&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9fd8d6d633ccb294d8ac229c312a9a7</data>
