  <data key="d12">1778875139</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="NeRF" target="NeuS">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">NeuS adapts its volume-rendering integral from NeRF and is motivated by inheriting NeRF's robust gradient-based optimization.</data>
  <data key="d9">adaptation,optimization</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-137c1bc42e741b7a6e96b6ddc476e477</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2106-10689/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778874757</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="NeRF" target="SDF-via-Volume-Rendering Paradigm">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The SDF-via-volume-rendering paradigm is described as having displaced original NeRF for high-fidelity multi-view surface reconstruction.</data>
  <data key="d9">displacement,methodological shift</data>
