  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">NeRF is attributed in the text to Mildenhall Et Al., 2020 as the earlier work that NeRF-W extends.&lt;SEP&gt;The standard NeRF used within Nerfies is explicitly attributed to Mildenhall et al., 2020.</data>
