<edge source="NeRF" target="DreamFusion">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">DreamFusion backpropagates per-view renderings of a NeRF so that the NeRF output looks like the prompt.&lt;SEP&gt;DreamFusion is described as using NeRF as its backbone.</data>
