  <data key="d8">Plenoxels is presented as a method for Novel View Synthesis that matches NeRF-quality results.&lt;SEP&gt;Plenoxels achieves NeRF-quality novel view synthesis at a fraction of the training cost.</data>
  <data key="d9">application,rendering quality,view synthesis</data>
