  <data key="d8">DROID-SLAM is presented in comparison on EuRoC, where aggressive motion is part of the protocol.&lt;SEP&gt;DROID-SLAM provides evaluation scripts for the EuRoC dataset.&lt;SEP&gt;DROID-SLAM is described as robust on the challenging EuRoC benchmark.</data>
  <data key="d9">aggressive motion,benchmark evaluation,benchmark performance,dataset support,evaluation,robustness</data>
