<edge source="DROID-SLAM" target="NICE-SLAM">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">NICE-SLAM is proposed as part of a head-to-head comparison alongside DROID-SLAM.&lt;SEP&gt;NICE-SLAM and DROID-SLAM are described as counterparts within the corpus because both address online SLAM with neural representations from opposite sides of the explicit-implicit spectrum.&lt;SEP&gt;NICE-SLAM benchmarks against DROID-SLAM as a deep-SLAM baseline.</data>
