  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">DeepV2D is described as the conceptual predecessor of DROID-SLAM.&lt;SEP&gt;DeepV2D is described as seeding the later DROID-SLAM line.&lt;SEP&gt;DROID-SLAM builds on the iterative-refinement idea introduced by DeepV2D.</data>
