<edge source="DreamFusion" target="Magic3D">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Magic3D is presented as a follow-on paper in the SDS line after DreamFusion, adding a coarse-to-fine schedule and a mesh-export second stage.&lt;SEP&gt;Magic3D is presented as a follow-up to DreamFusion and addresses DreamFusion's limitations in speed and low-resolution supervision.&lt;SEP&gt;DreamFusion is described as seeding the text-to-3D literature that includes Magic3D.</data>
  <data key="d9">SDS line,extension,follow-up,improvement,influence,literature</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b3dc42246e28acdc27923c03fab11c12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c63708e1adea212beb7d6e83516771&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-179a41f27c8e25c365ff0d8b13bddc43</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/weekly/2026-W18/synthesis.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2211-10440/paper.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2209-14988/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875234</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="DreamFusion" target="Zero-1-to-3">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Zero-1-to-3 is described as another development in the SDS line that adds camera-pose conditioning to the diffusion prior.&lt;SEP&gt;DreamFusion is described as seeding later single-image methods such as Zero-1-to-3.&lt;SEP&gt;Zero-1-to-3 is described as connecting the text-to-3D line represented by DreamFusion to single-image-to-3D work.</data>
  <data key="d9">SDS line,extension,influence,literature,research connection,text-to-3D</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b3dc42246e28acdc27923c03fab11c12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-179a41f27c8e25c365ff0d8b13bddc43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d4bb138a75a3adf4eebfac8bdf1be29</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/weekly/2026-W18/synthesis.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2209-14988/paper.md&lt;SEP&gt;examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2303-11328/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778876028</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
