</edge>
<edge source="Magic3D" target="Coarse-to-Fine NeRF-Then-Mesh Recipe">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Magic3D established the coarse-to-fine NeRF-then-mesh recipe for later text-to-3D work.</data>
