<edge source="GALA3D" target="GaussianSplatting Representation">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">GALA3D uses a layout-guided GaussianSplatting Representation to organise Gaussians into per-object groups for compositional scene modelling.</data>
  <data key="d9">compositional modelling,core representation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-8e84795d808a30ea730dabef6dcde2d3</data>
