</edge>
<edge source="GALA3D" target="Instance-Scene Compositional Optimisation Mechanism">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">GALA3D includes the Instance-Scene Compositional Optimisation Mechanism as a later stage that jointly refines the scene.</data>
  <data key="d9">joint refinement,pipeline stage</data>
