</edge>
<edge source="GALA3D" target="LLM-Generated Layout">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">GALA3D derives its scene structure from the LLM-Generated Layout, which also supports object movement, resizing, swapping, and re-optimisation.</data>
