<edge source="Nerfies" target="Dynamic View Synthesis from Dynamic Monocular Video">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Dynamic View Synthesis from Dynamic Monocular Video is described as the monocular companion alongside the dynamic line represented by Nerfies.&lt;SEP&gt;Dynamic View Synthesis from Dynamic Monocular Video is described as similar to Nerfies in the scale and controlled nature of evaluated captures.</data>
