<edge source="Nerfies" target="HyperNeRF">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">HyperNeRF extends the deformation field beyond Nerfies while still operating on the same short scale of input.&lt;SEP&gt;HyperNeRF extends the earlier Nerfies deformable radiance-field model to handle scenes with topological change.&lt;SEP&gt;HyperNeRF scenes are instructed to be organized in the Nerfies format.&lt;SEP&gt;HyperNeRF is described as the direct follow-up to Nerfies by the same team.</data>
  <data key="d9">data organization,dataset format,extension,follow-up work,method lineage,prior work,scale similarity</data>
