<edge source="Mip-NeRF" target="Cone">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Mip-NeRF replaces NeRF's thin ray with a cone whose apex is at the camera center and whose footprint matches the pixel.</data>
  <data key="d9">anti-aliasing,geometric representation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-24800bbb3bf5dc8182a3f3b86a0d5dad</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2103-13415/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875182</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF" target="Conical Frustums">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Mip-NeRF represents samples along the cone as a sequence of conical frustums rather than point samples.</data>
  <data key="d9">geometry,sampling representation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-24800bbb3bf5dc8182a3f3b86a0d5dad</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2103-13415/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875182</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF" target="Single Network">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Mip-NeRF uses a single network to consume features at any scale, collapsing the coarse and fine MLPs of vanilla NeRF.</data>
  <data key="d9">architecture,efficiency</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-24800bbb3bf5dc8182a3f3b86a0d5dad</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2103-13415/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875182</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF" target="Standard NeRF Synthetic Dataset">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Mip-NeRF reduces average error by 17 percent on the Standard NeRF Synthetic Dataset.</data>
  <data key="d9">error reduction,evaluation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-24800bbb3bf5dc8182a3f3b86a0d5dad</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2103-13415/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875182</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF" target="New Multiscale Variant">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Mip-NeRF reduces average error by 60 percent on the New Multiscale Variant introduced by the authors.</data>
  <data key="d9">error reduction,evaluation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-24800bbb3bf5dc8182a3f3b86a0d5dad</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2103-13415/paper.md</data>
