<edge source="NeuS" target="Signed Distance Function">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">NeuS represents geometry as the zero-level set of a signed distance function.&lt;SEP&gt;NeuS substitutes a signed distance function for the occupancy field used by UNISURF.&lt;SEP&gt;NeuS is described as representing geometry as a signed distance function.&lt;SEP&gt;NeuS represents geometry as a Signed Distance Function.</data>
  <data key="d9">geometry,geometry representation,refinement,representation,surface modeling,surface reconstruction</data>
