<edge source="NeuS" target="UNISURF">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Experiments report that NeuS produces sharper and more complete reconstructions than UNISURF.&lt;SEP&gt;UNISURF is described as a foundational reference for the surface-from-volume lineage that includes NeuS.&lt;SEP&gt;UNISURF is mentioned as related work alongside NeuS.&lt;SEP&gt;NeuS and UNISURF are described as sharing the same failure mode in challenging scenes.</data>
