<edge source="NeuS" target="Totoro97/NeuS">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Totoro97/NeuS is the released reference implementation of NeuS.&lt;SEP&gt;Totoro97/NeuS is the implementation associated with NeuS and is treated as the de-facto baseline.&lt;SEP&gt;Totoro97/NeuS is the official implementation of NeuS.&lt;SEP&gt;Totoro97/NeuS is identified as the official repository for the implementation of the NeuS method.</data>
  <data key="d9">baseline,codebase,implementation,official repository,repository</data>
