<edge source="Signed Distance Function" target="VolSDF">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">VolSDF substitutes a signed distance function for the occupancy field used by UNISURF.&lt;SEP&gt;VolSDF is described as representing geometry as a signed distance function.&lt;SEP&gt;VolSDF derives its volume density from a signed distance function and uses the signed distance function as its shape representation.</data>
  <data key="d9">density derivation,geometry,geometry representation,refinement,representation,surface reconstruction</data>
