<edge source="2D Text-to-Image Prior" target="3D-Aware Diffusion Prior">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Magic123 explicitly interpolates between the 2D text-to-image prior and the 3D-aware diffusion prior with a scalar trade-off parameter.</data>
  <data key="d9">prior interpolation,trade-off</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-11ccc947afd3d6b02019a4d324bd68d3</data>
