  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="3D-Aware Diffusion Prior" target="Scalar Trade-Off Parameter">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The scalar trade-off parameter controls how strongly Magic123 relies on the 3D-aware diffusion prior.</data>
  <data key="d9">interpolation,weighting</data>
