<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Synthesis-Based Bundle Adjustment">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">BARF frames its joint optimization problem as synthesis-based bundle adjustment within a single gradient-descent loop.</data>
  <data key="d9">formulation,optimization</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Classical Image Alignment">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper establishes a theoretical link between BARF's pixel synthesis and matching process and classical image alignment.</data>
  <data key="d9">analysis,theoretical link</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Coarse-to-Fine Annealing Schedule">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">BARF proposes a coarse-to-fine annealing schedule that masks out high positional-encoding frequencies early and progressively re-enables them.</data>
  <data key="d9">proposed fix,training strategy</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Extrinsic Pose">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">BARF applies the coarse-to-fine positional-encoding strategy specifically to extrinsic pose.</data>
  <data key="d9">application target,pose refinement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Synthetic Blender Scenes">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">BARF is evaluated on synthetic Blender scenes in its experiments.</data>
  <data key="d9">evaluation,experiments</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Real Forward-Facing Scenes">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">BARF is evaluated on real forward-facing scenes in its experiments.</data>
  <data key="d9">evaluation,experiments</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Pose-Free NeRF Training">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">By recovering poses and reconstructions from heavily perturbed or uninitialized cameras, BARF enables pose-free NeRF training.</data>
  <data key="d9">capability,enabling result</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Dense Reconstruction">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper connects radiance-field research to dense reconstruction.</data>
  <data key="d9">field linkage,research connection</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Pose-Refining NeRF Systems">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">BARF is described as a regular reference for later pose-refining NeRF systems.</data>
  <data key="d9">influence,reference</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="BARF: Bundle-Adjusting Neural Radiance Fields" target="Gaussian-Splatting Systems">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">BARF is described as a regular reference for later Gaussian-splatting systems.</data>
  <data key="d9">influence,reference</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
