</edge>
<edge source="Classical Image Alignment" target="Photometric Residual">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper explains the alignment connection through first-order analysis on the photometric residual.</data>
  <data key="d9">alignment,first-order formulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875754</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Classical Image Alignment" target="Lucas-Kanade Alignment">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Lucas-Kanade alignment is presented as a robust classical image alignment method whose coarse-to-fine strategy motivates BARF's design.</data>
  <data key="d9">method lineage,robustness</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875754</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="High-Frequency Sinusoidal Positional Encoding" target="Local Minima">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The spiky landscape caused by high-frequency positional encoding makes bundle adjustment fall into local minima.</data>
  <data key="d9">instability,optimization failure</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875754</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="High-Frequency Sinusoidal Positional Encoding" target="Coarse-to-Fine Annealing Schedule">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The annealing schedule operates by temporarily suppressing high-frequency positional-encoding bands and restoring them later in training.</data>
  <data key="d9">frequency control,masking</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-252e33536ee596bbdc69a5c1521289c2</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2104-06405/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Coarse-to-Fine Annealing Schedule" target="Positional-Encoding Frequencies">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The coarse-to-fine annealing schedule is applied to the positional-encoding frequencies of the deformation network.</data>
  <data key="d9">annealing,encoding control</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-640801c18546ebea4632cd80bbad0951</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2011-12948/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778876157</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Coarse-to-Fine Annealing Schedule" target="Dynamic-NeRF Literature">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The coarse-to-fine encoding schedule recurs across the dynamic-NeRF literature in the corpus.</data>
  <data key="d9">literature influence,recurrence</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-640801c18546ebea4632cd80bbad0951</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2011-12948/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778876157</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF 360: Unbounded Anti-Aliased Neural Radiance Fields" target="Non-Linear Scene Parameterization">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper introduces non-linear scene parameterization as one of its three main contributions.</data>
  <data key="d9">contribution,method</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d0dff9058b6eb6ab9730d5170f51b92d</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2111-12077/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF 360: Unbounded Anti-Aliased Neural Radiance Fields" target="Online Distillation Scheme">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper introduces an online distillation scheme to improve hierarchical sampling efficiency in large scenes.</data>
  <data key="d9">contribution,method</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d0dff9058b6eb6ab9730d5170f51b92d</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2111-12077/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF 360: Unbounded Anti-Aliased Neural Radiance Fields" target="Distortion-Based Regularizer">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper introduces a distortion-based regularizer to suppress rendering artifacts in unbounded captures.</data>
  <data key="d9">contribution,regularization</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d0dff9058b6eb6ab9730d5170f51b92d</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2111-12077/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF 360: Unbounded Anti-Aliased Neural Radiance Fields" target="Unbounded 360-Degree Scenes">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper targets unbounded 360-degree scenes such as outdoor environments and large indoor spaces.</data>
  <data key="d9">application,scene regime</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d0dff9058b6eb6ab9730d5170f51b92d</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2111-12077/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF 360: Unbounded Anti-Aliased Neural Radiance Fields" target="Mip-NeRF360 Dataset">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper introduces the Mip-NeRF360 dataset as a new 360-degree benchmark.</data>
  <data key="d9">benchmark introduction,evaluation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d0dff9058b6eb6ab9730d5170f51b92d</data>
  <data key="d11">examples/demo-corpus/data/research/papers/arxiv-2111-12077/paper.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1778875755</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Mip-NeRF 360: Unbounded Anti-Aliased Neural Radiance Fields" target="Mean-Squared Error">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The paper reports a 57% reduction in mean-squared error relative to Mip-NeRF.</data>
