<edge source="Viewpoint-Conditional Diffusion Model" target="Stable-Diffusion-Style 2D Diffusion Model">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The viewpoint-conditional diffusion model is obtained by fine-tuning a Stable-Diffusion-style 2D diffusion model.</data>
  <data key="d9">backbone adaptation,fine-tuning</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7d4bb138a75a3adf4eebfac8bdf1be29</data>
